data.description: Nestled on a Generous 0.5-acre lot in the heart of Mena, this Exquisite Residence offers a perfect blend of Modern Comfort and Timeless Elegance. With 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a host of custom features, this home on Averitt Ave is a true gem that you'll want to make your own. The charming exterior sets the tone for what lies within, offering a warm welcome to residents and guests alike. The interior of this home boasts a thoughtful split floor plan, providing both privacy and functionality. What's more, this home is fully handicap accessible, ensuring comfort and convenience for all residents. With 9-foot ceilings throughout the house, this space feels open, airy, and filled with natural light. The Dream Kitchen features custom cabinetry that not only provides ample storage. The engineered hardwood floors not only enhance the overall aesthetic but also make cleaning a breeze. The master bedroom is a true retreat with its tray ceiling, offering an extra layer of luxury. The en-suite bathroom is equally impressive, featuring a full bath, separate shower, and double vanity – a haven of relaxation after a long day.
